Example for showing C code coverage and complexity metrics.
To see code complexity, run the following:

   pmccabe *.c | sort -nr | head -10

To see test coverage, run the following:

   cover -t

To check for naughty words (like TODO), run the following:

   make test


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module demonstrates these other modules and libraries:

  Devel::Cover
  Perl::Metrics::Simple
  Test::Fixme

